y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d48e7d3e27d4f35c638832baa9e266c105c8f67","tid":694922,"uid":56824,"like":88,"dislike":6,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T21:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa0c0db99fc713f441ae56819aa6588edb8372ab","tid":694922,"uid":64564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T22:03:02.000Z","msg":"係咪真係會死嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44aea5f04bd2c5b5ad5b52cf4583ecce4ee59ea","tid":694922,"uid":111253,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T22:04:57.000Z","msg":"曲赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  曲尺"},{"pid":"ae5f30cc193572dad374a70619d36f36c5ac6f1d","tid":694922,"uid":139224,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T22:26:13.000Z","msg":"屌你，更新mk仔都出到道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b00590d545be04c81165848167925fe6b3629ca","tid":694922,"uid":63119,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"quote":{"pid":"ae5f30cc193572dad374a70619d36f36c5ac6f1d","tid":694922,"uid":139224,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T22:26:13.000Z","msg":"屌你，更新mk仔都出到道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T22:38:22.000Z","msg":"佢話自己出道啫<br />\n由頭到尾都係自己捧自己<br />\n咪即係章魚城個啲人囉"},{"pid":"60acb740aa22b2f46b169f7c3af99b84514d896b","tid":694922,"uid":21045,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T23:34:46.000Z","msg":"無人想討論佢呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"fca2dbe3319a64963bd094445d1318aa426249c3","tid":694922,"uid":119135,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T23:35:21.000Z","msg":"周永痕正常D"},{"pid":"cbe06b5f791585456902247f6053a31396e413f2","tid":694922,"uid":49163,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"tl好波<img src=\"/asset